---

<section id="problema" class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-white via-slate-50 to-white dark:from-slate-900 dark:via-slate-800 dark:to-slate-900 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative elements -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-32 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-transparent dark:from-slate-900 dark:to-transparent"></div>
  <div class="absolute -left-32 top-1/4 w-64 h-64 bg-red-200/10 dark:bg-red-900/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="absolute -right-32 bottom-1/4 w-64 h-64 bg-orange-200/10 dark:bg-orange-900/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Headline -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-red-100/80 dark:bg-red-900/50 text-red-700 dark:text-red-300 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">
        El problema
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white leading-tight">
        La pesadilla de la nómina<br class="hidden sm:block" /> termina hoy.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Copy -->
    <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
      ¿Sigues contratando personas para que copien y peguen respuestas en WhatsApp? Estás quemando dinero. El empleado promedio comete errores, olvida seguimientos, exige beneficios y se cansa. Si no respondes rápido, tu competencia lo hará. <span class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-semibold">Deja de ser el rehén de la ineficiencia humana</span> en tu embudo de ventas.
    </p>

    <!-- Warning box - enhanced -->
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto p-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-50 to-orange-50 dark:from-red-950/50 dark:to-orange-950/50 border-l-4 border-red-500 rounded-2xl shadow-lg shadow-red-100 dark:shadow-none">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-900/50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 dark:text-red-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-red-800 dark:text-red-300 font-medium">
          Por cada lead que no respondes en 5 minutos, <span class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 font-bold">pierdes un cliente potencial</span>. El 78% de los prospectos compran al primer respondedor.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
